{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id05951370-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d","identifier":"/us/usc/t19/s2021"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2021"},"text":"§ 2021.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" General authority","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A petition may be filed for tariff adjustment or for a determination of eligibility to apply for adjustment assistance under title III of the Trade Expansion Act of 1962 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1901"},"text":"19 U.S.C. 1901","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] as though the reduction or elimination of a duty proclaimed by the President pursuant to section 2011 or 2012 of this title were a concession granted under a trade agreement referred to in section 301 of the Trade Expansion Act of 1962 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1901"},"text":"19 U.S.C. 1901","children":[],"tail":"]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id05951371-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/283/tIII/s301"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–283, title III, § 301","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/1018"},"text":"79 Stat. 1018","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id05951372-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id05951373-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id05951374-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Trade Expansion Act of 1962, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/794"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–794","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-11"},"text":"Oct. 11, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/872"},"text":"76 Stat. 872","children":[],"tail":". Title III of the Trade Expansion Act of 1962 is classified generally to subchapter III (§ 1901 et seq.) of chapter 7 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1801"},"text":"section 1801 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 301 of the Trade Expansion Act of 1962, referred to in text, was classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1901"},"text":"section 1901 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/618/tVI/s602/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–618, title VI, § 602(d)","children":[],"tail":", (e), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-03"},"text":"Jan. 3, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/2072"},"text":"88 Stat. 2072","children":[],"tail":". See section 2251 et seq. of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2012"},"text":"Section 2012 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, was omitted from the Code."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id05951375-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The words “subject to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2022"},"text":"section 2022 of this title","children":[],"tail":"” omitted in view of the omission of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2022"},"text":"section 2022 of this title","children":[],"tail":", which provided special authority after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1965","children":[],"tail":", and before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1968","children":[],"tail":", for filing of petitions for determination by the President of eligibility to apply for adjustment assistance."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
